title: Sora no ana (2001)
description:
Sora no ana (2001)
127 min - Drama - 29 September 2001 (Japan)
Ratings: 6,8/10 from 144 users 

The film tells the story of a Drive-In worker and a young tramp 
who has been left alone by her boyfriend somewhere in Hokkaido. 
Things seem to work out at the beginning but as time goes by 
the newly formed relationship between the tramp 
and the Drive-In worker starts to show the workers harmful 
will of possession, which finally leads to the somehow sad 
but also optimistically interpretable ending.
